<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Liquidación Asesora del Hogar</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --cream:#FAF7F2; --warm:#F0E8D8; --dark:#1A1410; --muted:#6B5E52;
    --accent:#C4522A; --border:#D9CFC4; --card:#FFFFFF;
    --success:#2A6B5B; --danger:#C4522A; --info:#2A5B8B;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  body{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;background:var(--cream);color:var(--dark);min-height:100vh}

  /* HEADER */
  .app-header{background:var(--dark);color:var(--cream);padding:16px 28px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .app-header h1{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.3rem}
  .app-header small{font-size:0.68rem;opacity:0.5;display:block;margin-top:2px}
  .header-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .db-status{font-size:0.71rem;padding:4px 11px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap}
  .db-ok{background:#1a3d2e;color:#5dffc0} .db-err{background:#3d1a1a;color:#ff9999} .db-loading{background:#2a2520;color:#ffd580}

  /* WORKER SELECTOR */
  .worker-bar{background:var(--warm);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:10px 28px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .worker-bar label{font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.4px;white-space:nowrap}
  .worker-bar select{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:7px 11px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.87rem;background:#fff;color:var(--dark);max-width:280px}
  .worker-bar select:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--accent)}

  /* TABS */
  .tabs{background:#fff;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;padding:0 20px;overflow-x:auto}
  .tab-btn{padding:12px 16px;border:none;background:none;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.81rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;border-bottom:3px solid transparent;white-space:nowrap;transition:all 0.2s}
  .tab-btn:hover{color:var(--dark)} .tab-btn.active{color:var(--accent);border-bottom-color:var(--accent);font-weight:600}

  /* CONTENT */
  .tab-content{display:none;padding:22px 28px;max-width:980px;margin:0 auto}
  .tab-content.active{display:block}

  /* CARDS */
  .card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:16px}
  .card-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:14px;color:var(--dark);border-bottom:1px solid var(--warm);padding-bottom:9px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px}

  /* FORMS */
  .form-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:12px}
  .form-row.three{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr}
  .form-row.four{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr}
  .form-group{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px}
  .form-group.full{grid-column:1/-1}
  label{font-size:0.73rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px}
  input,select,textarea{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:9px 11px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.87rem;background:var(--cream);color:var(--dark);transition:border-color 0.2s;width:100%}
  input:focus,select:focus,textarea:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--accent);background:#fff}
  input[readonly]{background:var(--warm);color:var(--muted)}
  textarea{resize:vertical;min-height:66px}

  /* BUTTONS */
  .btn{padding:9px 17px;border:none;border-radius:8px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:0.83rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
  .btn-primary{background:var(--accent);color:#fff} .btn-primary:hover{background:#a8451f}
  .btn-secondary{background:var(--dark);color:#fff} .btn-secondary:hover{background:#2d2520}
  .btn-outline{background:transparent;color:var(--accent);border:2px solid var(--accent)} .btn-outline:hover{background:var(--accent);color:#fff}
  .btn-success{background:var(--success);color:#fff} .btn-success:hover{background:#1e5042}
  .btn-ghost{background:var(--warm);color:var(--dark);border:1px solid var(--border)} .btn-ghost:hover{background:var(--border)}
  .btn-sm{padding:6px 12px;font-size:0.77rem}
  .btn-danger-sm{background:#fde8e8;color:#c0392b;border:none;border-radius:6px;padding:4px 9px;font-size:0.73rem;cursor:pointer;font-weight:600}

  /* ASESORAS LIST */
  .asesor-card{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:14px 16px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:10px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;background:#fff}
  .asesor-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent);background:#fff8f5}
  .asesor-card.selected{border-color:var(--accent);border-width:2px;background:#fff5f2}
  .asesor-avatar{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);color:#fff;font-size:1.2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;flex-shrink:0}
  .asesor-avatar.color2{background:var(--success)} .asesor-avatar.color3{background:var(--info)} .asesor-avatar.color4{background:#7b5ea7}
  .asesor-info{flex:1}
  .asesor-info strong{font-size:0.92rem}
  .asesor-info p{font-size:0.76rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px}
  .asesor-actions{display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center}
  .badge{display:inline-block;background:var(--success);color:#fff;font-size:0.67rem;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:6px;vertical-align:middle}
  .badge-sel{background:var(--accent)}

  /* PERFIL MINI */
  .perfil-mini{display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:center;background:var(--warm);border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:14px}
  .perfil-mini h3{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1rem}
  .perfil-mini p{font-size:0.77rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:3px}

  /* LIQUIDACION */
  .liq-preview{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:14px}
  .liq-header{background:var(--dark);color:var(--cream);padding:20px 26px;text-align:center}
  .liq-header h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.12rem;letter-spacing:2px}
  .liq-header p{font-size:0.75rem;opacity:0.5;margin-top:4px}
  .liq-body{padding:20px 26px}
  .liq-worker{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin-bottom:18px;padding-bottom:14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--warm)}
  .liq-worker-info h3{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:0.93rem}
  .liq-worker-info p{font-size:0.76rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:3px}
  .liq-section{margin-bottom:12px}
  .liq-section-title{font-size:0.66rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:6px}
  .liq-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:6px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f5f0e8;font-size:0.85rem}
  .liq-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .pos{font-weight:600;color:var(--success)} .neg{font-weight:600;color:var(--danger)}
  .liq-totals{background:var(--warm);border-radius:8px;padding:12px 14px;margin-top:12px}
  .liq-total-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:5px 0;font-weight:600;font-size:0.86rem}
  .liq-total-row.final{font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--accent);border-top:2px solid var(--border);padding-top:10px;margin-top:5px}
  .liq-footer{padding:16px 26px;border-top:1px solid var(--warm);display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px;font-size:0.77rem;color:var(--muted);text-align:center}
  .firma-line{border-top:1px solid var(--dark);margin-top:36px;padding-top:7px;font-size:0.71rem}
  /* Costo empleador — solo pantalla, nunca en impresión */
  .employer-costs{background:#fff5f2;border:1px solid #f0c8b8;border-radius:8px;padding:13px;margin-top:12px}
  .employer-costs h4{font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--accent);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;margin-bottom:9px;font-weight:700}
  .cost-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:4px 0;font-size:0.81rem;border-bottom:1px solid #f5ddd4}
  .cost-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;font-weight:700}

  /* DÍAS TRABAJADOS */
  .dias-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px}
  .dias-result{background:var(--dark);color:var(--cream);border-radius:12px;padding:20px;text-align:center;margin-bottom:14px}
  .dias-big{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:3rem;color:#ffd580;line-height:1}
  .dias-lbl{font-size:0.76rem;opacity:0.6;margin-top:5px}
  .resumen-dias{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:8px;margin-top:12px}
  .resumen-item{background:var(--warm);border-radius:8px;padding:10px;text-align:center}
  .resumen-item .rv{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.4rem;color:var(--accent)}
  .resumen-item .rl{font-size:0.69rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px}
  .ausencia-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:var(--warm);border-radius:7px;padding:8px 11px;margin-bottom:6px}
  .ausencia-item .ai{flex:1}
  .ausencia-item .ai strong{font-size:0.84rem}
  .ausencia-item .ai span{font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--muted);display:block}
  .ausencia-item .ad{font-weight:700;color:var(--danger);font-size:0.93rem;min-width:34px;text-align:right}
  .tipo-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:0.64rem;font-weight:700;padding:1px 7px;border-radius:9px;margin-left:4px}
  .tipo-injustificada{background:#fde8e8;color:#c0392b} .tipo-justificada{background:#e8f5e9;color:#27ae60}
  .tipo-licencia{background:#e3f2fd;color:#1565c0} .tipo-vacaciones{background:#fff3e0;color:#e65100}
  .tipo-feriado{background:#f3e5f5;color:#7b1fa2} .tipo-permiso{background:#fce4ec;color:#880e4f}
  .escenario-btns{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px}

  /* HISTORIAL */
  .hist-filters{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:14px;align-items:center}
  .hist-filters select,.hist-filters input{max-width:200px;padding:8px 10px;font-size:0.83rem}
  .history-item{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:12px 14px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:8px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s}
  .history-item:hover{border-color:var(--accent);background:#fff8f5}
  .history-month{font-weight:600;font-size:0.88rem}
  .history-net{color:var(--success);font-weight:700;font-size:0.95rem}

  /* INDICADORES */
  .ind-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:0.83rem}
  .ind-table th{background:var(--dark);color:var(--cream);padding:9px 11px;text-align:left;font-weight:600}
  .ind-table td{padding:8px 11px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--warm)}
  .ind-table tr:hover td{background:var(--cream)}
  .hl{font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)}

  /* VACACIONES */
  .vac-box{background:var(--warm);border-radius:10px;padding:16px;margin-top:12px}

  /* CALLOUT */
  .callout{border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:11px 14px;font-size:0.81rem;margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.5}
  .callout.info{background:#eaf5f1;border-left:4px solid var(--success)}
  .callout.warn{background:#fff5f0;border-left:4px solid var(--accent)}
  .callout.blue{background:#eef4ff;border-left:4px solid var(--info)}

  /* MODAL */
  .modal-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.72);z-index:999;overflow:auto;padding:20px}
  .modal-box{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;background:#fff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden}
  .modal-actions{padding:14px 18px;display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:flex-end;border-top:1px solid #eee}

  /* TOAST */
  .toast{position:fixed;bottom:20px;right:20px;background:var(--dark);color:var(--cream);padding:11px 18px;border-radius:9px;font-size:0.85rem;z-index:9999;transform:translateY(70px);opacity:0;transition:all 0.3s;pointer-events:none;max-width:280px}
  .toast.show{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1}
  .tok{border-left:4px solid #5dffc0} .terr{border-left:4px solid #ff9999}

  /* EMPTY STATE */
  .empty-state{text-align:center;padding:36px;color:var(--muted);font-size:0.88rem}
  .empty-state .icon{font-size:2.5rem;display:block;margin-bottom:10px}

  /* PRINT — solo liquidación limpia */
  @media print {
    .tabs,.app-header,.worker-bar,.btn,.no-print,.modal-actions,.toast,.employer-costs{display:none!important}
    .tab-content{display:block!important;padding:0}
    .liq-preview{border:none;box-shadow:none}
    .liq-body,.liq-header,.liq-footer{-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;print-color-adjust:exact}
    body{background:#fff}
  }

  @media (max-width:640px){
    .tab-content{padding:14px}
    .form-row,.form-row.three,.form-row.four,.dias-grid,.resumen-dias{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .liq-footer{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .worker-bar{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="app-header">
  <div>
    <h1>🏠 Liquidación Asesora del Hogar</h1>
    <small>Sistema de remuneraciones · Chile 2026</small>
  </div>
  <div class="header-right">
    <span class="db-status db-loading" id="db-status">● Conectando…</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SELECTOR GLOBAL DE ASESORA -->
<div class="worker-bar" id="worker-bar">
  <label>Asesora activa:</label>
  <select id="selector-asesora" onchange="cambiarAsesora(this.value)">
    <option value="">— Selecciona una asesora —</option>
  </select>
  <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" onclick="showTab('asesoras',null)">👥 Gestionar</button>
  <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="nuevaAsesora()">+ Nueva Asesora</button>
</div>

<div class="tabs">
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('asesoras',this)">👥 Asesoras</button>
  <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="showTab('liquidacion',this)">📄 Liquidación</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('dias',this)">📅 Días Trabajados</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('vacaciones',this)">🌴 Vacaciones</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('indicadores',this)">📊 Indicadores</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('historial',this)">📁 Historial</button>
</div>

<!-- ====== TAB: GESTIÓN ASESORAS ====== -->
<div id="tab-asesoras" class="tab-content">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">
      <span>👥 Asesoras Registradas</span>
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="nuevaAsesora()">+ Agregar Nueva</button>
    </div>
    <div id="lista-asesoras"><div class="empty-state"><span class="icon">👤</span>No hay asesoras registradas aún.</div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- FORMULARIO AGREGAR/EDITAR -->
  <div class="card" id="form-asesora-card" style="display:none">
    <div class="card-title" id="form-asesora-titulo">➕ Nueva Asesora</div>
    <input type="hidden" id="a-id">

    <div class="card" style="background:var(--warm);border:none;padding:14px;margin-bottom:0">
      <div style="font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px">Información Personal</div>
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-group full"><label>Nombre Completo *</label><input type="text" id="a-nombre" placeholder="Nombre y Apellidos"></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>RUT *</label><input type="text" id="a-rut" placeholder="12.345.678-9" oninput="fmtRut(this)"></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>Teléfono</label><input type="tel" id="a-telefono" placeholder="+56 9 1234 5678"></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>Email</label><input type="email" id="a-email" placeholder="correo@email.com"></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>Fecha de Nacimiento</label><input type="date" id="a-nacimiento"></div>
      </div>

      <div style="font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;margin:14px 0 10px">Contrato y Remuneración</div>
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-group"><label>Fecha de Ingreso *</label><input type="date" id="a-ingreso" oninput="calcAnt()"></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>Antigüedad</label><input type="text" id="a-antiguedad" readonly></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>Tipo Contrato</label>
          <select id="a-contrato"><option value="indefinido">Plazo Indefinido</option><option value="fijo">Plazo Fijo</option></select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>Modalidad</label>
          <select id="a-modalidad"><option value="puertas_afuera">Puertas Afuera</option><option value="puertas_adentro">Puertas Adentro</option><option value="por_horas">Por Horas / Días</option></select>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-row three">
        <div class="form-group"><label>Sueldo Base * (mín. $539.000)</label><input type="number" id="a-sueldo" value="539000" min="539000"></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>Movilización</label><input type="number" id="a-movilizacion" value="78000" min="0"></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>Colación</label><input type="number" id="a-colacion" value="78000" min="0"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-group"><label>AFP</label>
          <select id="a-afp">
            <option value="10.46" data-nombre="Uno">AFP Uno (10,46%)</option>
            <option value="11.44" data-nombre="Capital">AFP Capital (11,44%)</option>
            <option value="11.44" data-nombre="Cuprum">AFP Cuprum (11,44%)</option>
            <option value="11.27" data-nombre="Habitat">AFP Habitat (11,27%)</option>
            <option value="11.16" data-nombre="PlanVital">AFP PlanVital (11,16%)</option>
            <option value="11.45" data-nombre="Provida">AFP Provida (11,45%)</option>
            <option value="10.58" data-nombre="Modelo">AFP Modelo (10,58%)</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>Años Totales Trabajados (todos empleadores)</label><input type="number" id="a-anios-totales" value="0" min="0"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group" style="margin-top:4px"><label>Notas / Acuerdos</label><textarea id="a-notas" placeholder="Ej: No trabaja festivos, incluye almuerzo…"></textarea></div>
    </div>

    <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:flex-end;margin-top:14px;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="cancelarFormAsesora()">Cancelar</button>
      <button class="btn btn-success" onclick="guardarAsesora()">💾 Guardar Asesora</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====== TAB: LIQUIDACIÓN ====== -->
<div id="tab-liquidacion" class="tab-content active">
  <div class="callout warn" id="liq-warn-sin-asesora">
    ⚠️ <strong>Selecciona una asesora</strong> en la barra superior para generar su liquidación.
  </div>
  <div id="liq-perfil-mini" style="display:none"></div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">📅 Parámetros del Mes</div>
    <div class="form-row four">
      <div class="form-group"><label>Período</label><input type="month" id="periodo" oninput="calcular()"></div>
      <div class="form-group"><label>Días Trabajados</label><input type="number" id="dias" value="30" min="1" max="31" oninput="calcular()"></div>
      <div class="form-group"><label>AFP</label>
        <select id="afp" onchange="calcular()">
          <option value="10.46" data-nombre="Uno">AFP Uno</option>
          <option value="11.44" data-nombre="Capital">AFP Capital</option>
          <option value="11.44" data-nombre="Cuprum">AFP Cuprum</option>
          <option value="11.27" data-nombre="Habitat">AFP Habitat</option>
          <option value="11.16" data-nombre="PlanVital">AFP PlanVital</option>
          <option value="11.45" data-nombre="Provida">AFP Provida</option>
          <option value="10.58" data-nombre="Modelo">AFP Modelo</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group"><label>Tipo Contrato</label>
        <select id="contrato" onchange="calcular()"><option value="indefinido">Plazo Indefinido</option><option value="fijo">Plazo Fijo</option></select>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">💰 Haberes del Mes</div>
    <div class="form-row three">
      <div class="form-group"><label>Sueldo Base</label><input type="number" id="sueldo" value="539000" oninput="calcular()"></div>
      <div class="form-group"><label>Movilización</label><input type="number" id="movilizacion" value="78000" oninput="calcular()"></div>
      <div class="form-group"><label>Colación</label><input type="number" id="colacion" value="78000" oninput="calcular()"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-row three">
      <div class="form-group"><label>Horas Extra</label><input type="number" id="horasExtra" value="0" oninput="calcular()"></div>
      <div class="form-group"><label>Bono / Gratificación</label><input type="number" id="bono" value="0" oninput="calcular()"></div>
      <div class="form-group"><label>Descuento Adicional (anticipo, etc.)</label><input type="number" id="descAdicional" value="0" oninput="calcular()"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="resultado-liquidacion"></div>

  <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:flex-end;flex-wrap:wrap" class="no-print">
    <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="imprimirLiq()">🖨️ PDF / Imprimir</button>
    <button class="btn btn-success" onclick="guardarLiquidacion()">💾 Guardar en Supabase</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====== TAB: DÍAS TRABAJADOS ====== -->
<div id="tab-dias" class="tab-content">
  <div class="callout blue">📅 Calcula los días a pagar según distintos escenarios: ingreso parcial, ausencias, licencias, feriados trabajados, etc.</div>
  <div class="dias-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">📆 Período y Jornada</div>
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group"><label>Mes / Año</label><input type="month" id="d-periodo" oninput="calcDias()"></div>
          <div class="form-group"><label>Base de Cálculo</label>
            <select id="d-jornada" onchange="calcDias()"><option value="30">30 días (estándar)</option><option value="real">Días reales del mes</option></select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group"><label>¿Ingresó este mes?</label>
            <select id="d-ingreso-parcial" onchange="toggleIngrParcial();calcDias()">
              <option value="no">No (mes completo)</option>
              <option value="si">Sí (ingreso a mitad de mes)</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group" id="d-ingreso-fecha-grp" style="display:none">
            <label>Fecha de Ingreso al Trabajo</label><input type="date" id="d-ingreso-fecha" oninput="calcDias()">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">➕ Registrar Incidencia</div>
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group"><label>Tipo</label>
            <select id="d-tipo">
              <option value="injustificada">Inasistencia Injustificada</option>
              <option value="justificada">Inasistencia Justificada</option>
              <option value="licencia">Licencia Médica</option>
              <option value="vacaciones">Vacaciones</option>
              <option value="feriado">Feriado Trabajado (+días)</option>
              <option value="permiso">Permiso Sin Goce</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group"><label>Descripción</label><input type="text" id="d-desc" placeholder="Ej: Licencia código B"></div>
          <div class="form-group"><label>Desde</label><input type="date" id="d-desde"></div>
          <div class="form-group"><label>Hasta</label><input type="date" id="d-hasta"></div>
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="addAusencia()">➕ Agregar</button>
      </div>
      <div class="card" id="card-ausencias" style="display:none">
        <div class="card-title">📋 Incidencias del Mes</div>
        <div id="lista-ausencias"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">📊 Resultado</div>
        <div class="dias-result">
          <div class="dias-big" id="d-resultado">30</div>
          <div class="dias-lbl">días a pagar</div>
        </div>
        <div class="resumen-dias">
          <div class="resumen-item"><div class="rv" id="d-base">30</div><div class="rl">Días base</div></div>
          <div class="resumen-item"><div class="rv" id="d-ausentes">0</div><div class="rl">Ausentes</div></div>
          <div class="resumen-item"><div class="rv" id="d-extra">0</div><div class="rl">Extra (+)</div></div>
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-success" style="margin-top:12px;width:100%;justify-content:center" onclick="usarDias()">✅ Usar en Liquidación</button>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">📝 Detalle</div>
        <div id="d-detalle" style="font-size:0.82rem;line-height:1.85;color:var(--muted)">—</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">⚡ Escenarios Rápidos</div>
        <div class="escenario-btns">
          <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="escenario('completo')">📅 Mes completo (30 días)</button>
          <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="escenario('ingreso15')">📅 Ingresó el día 15</button>
          <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="escenario('ingreso20')">📅 Ingresó el día 20</button>
          <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="escenario('aus1')">📅 Mes completo − 1 día injustificado</button>
          <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="escenario('licencia5')">📅 Licencia médica 5 días</button>
          <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="escenario('licencia7')">📅 Licencia médica 7 días</button>
          <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="escenario('vacaciones5')">📅 5 días de vacaciones</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====== TAB: VACACIONES ====== -->
<div id="tab-vacaciones" class="tab-content">
  <div class="callout info">
    <strong>Vacaciones:</strong> 15 días hábiles con remuneración íntegra al completar 1 año. Sábados, domingos y festivos no cuentan.
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">🌴 Cálculo de Vacaciones</div>
    <div class="form-row">
      <div class="form-group"><label>Fecha de Ingreso</label><input type="date" id="v-ingreso" oninput="calcVac()"></div>
      <div class="form-group"><label>Fecha Inicio Vacaciones</label><input type="date" id="v-inicio" oninput="calcVac()"></div>
      <div class="form-group"><label>Sueldo Base</label><input type="number" id="v-sueldo" value="539000" oninput="calcVac()"></div>
      <div class="form-group"><label>Años Totales (feriado progresivo)</label><input type="number" id="v-anios" value="0" min="0" oninput="calcVac()"></div>
    </div>
    <div id="v-resultado" class="vac-box" style="display:none"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">📚 Normativa</div>
    <div style="font-size:0.83rem;line-height:1.78;color:var(--muted)">
      <p><strong style="color:var(--dark)">Feriado Legal:</strong> 15 días hábiles/año. Sábados, domingos y festivos no cuentan.</p><br>
      <p><strong style="color:var(--dark)">Feriado Progresivo:</strong> Con más de 10 años (cualquier empleador), 1 día adicional por cada 3 nuevos años.</p><br>
      <p><strong style="color:var(--dark)">Fraccionamiento:</strong> Solo el exceso sobre 10 días hábiles, de mutuo acuerdo.</p><br>
      <p><strong style="color:var(--dark)">Compensación en dinero:</strong> Solo al terminar la relación laboral (finiquito).</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

